---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AdSlot from '../components/AdSlot.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Medical Disclaimer"
  description="Important medical disclaimer for Paramedical Knowledge Hub. This site provides educational information only."
>
  <div class="disclaimer-page">
    <article class="disclaimer-content">
      <h1>Medical Disclaimer</h1>

      <AdSlot position="top-page" />

      <div class="disclaimer-box">
        <p>
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
            year: 'numeric',
            month: 'long',
            day: 'numeric',
          })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>No Medical Advice</h2>
        <p>
          The information provided on Paramedical Knowledge Hub (the "Website") is for educational
          and informational purposes only. It is not intended as a substitute for professional
          medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of your physician or
          other qualified health provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical
          condition.
        </p>
        <p>
          Never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of something
          you have read on this Website. If you think you may have a medical emergency, call your
          doctor or emergency services immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Not a Healthcare Provider</h2>
        <p>
          Paramedical Knowledge Hub is not a healthcare provider. We do not provide medical
          services, diagnosis, or treatment. The content on this Website is general in nature and
          may not apply to your specific circumstances.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>No Doctor-Patient Relationship</h2>
        <p>
          Your use of this Website does not create a doctor-patient relationship. The information
          provided is not personalized medical advice. You should not act or refrain from acting
          based on any information contained on this Website without first seeking appropriate
          professional advice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>
          While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, medical knowledge is
          constantly evolving. We make no representations or warranties of any kind, express or
          implied, about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or availability of
          the information contained on this Website.
        </p>
        <p>
          Any reliance you place on such information is strictly at your own risk. We disclaim all
          liability and responsibility arising from any reliance placed on such materials by you or
          any other visitor to the Website, or by anyone who may be informed of any of its
          contents.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Content and Links</h2>
        <p>
          This Website may contain links to third-party websites or resources. We are not
          responsible for the content, accuracy, or opinions expressed on such websites. The
          inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by Paramedical Knowledge Hub.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, Paramedical Knowledge Hub, its owners, operators,
          authors, and contributors shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental,
          special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenues, whether
          incurred directly or indirectly, or any loss of data, use, goodwill, or other intangible
          losses resulting from your use of this Website or reliance on any information contained
          herein.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Individual Responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          You are solely responsible for your own health decisions. The information on this Website
          should not be used to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease or health condition.
          Always consult with a qualified healthcare professional before making any changes to your
          health regimen, diet, exercise routine, or medication.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Emergency Situations</h2>
        <p>
          If you are experiencing a medical emergency, do not use this Website. Call your local
          emergency services (e.g., 911 in the United States) or go to the nearest emergency room
          immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this disclaimer or the content on this Website, please{' '}
          <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. However, please note that we cannot provide medical
          advice or answer specific health-related questions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="acknowledgment">
        <p>
          <strong>By using this Website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree
          to this Medical Disclaimer.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <AdSlot position="bottom-page" />
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .disclaimer-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .disclaimer-content {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .disclaimer-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    background: #fef3c7;
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .disclaimer-content section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .disclaimer-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .disclaimer-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #374151;
  }

  .acknowledgment {
    background: #fee2e2;
    border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .acknowledgment p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #991b1b;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .disclaimer-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .disclaimer-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>

